===== preserved non-authoritative attempts
History and commit 12052949752cd3c88511597827cd74238fe6b866 preserve the earlier attempt transcripts. They are not authoritative evidence. Rejected attempts included:
- a warm run without visibly explicit guards;
- a zero-filter resumable-render fixture;
- cancellation and wait-render assertions that exposed real contract mismatches before correction;
- drivers whose live process environment lacked one or more required guards;
- validation invalidated by concurrent source/test formatting or rename commits;
- direct-driver shell bug `label: unbound variable`;
- workspace-wide formatting red on inherited out-of-declaration files;
- dependency-boundary invocation outside the pinned dev shell.
The premature evidence commit recorded 12 passes without a guard manifest and omitted the Persisted and SkippedLockTimeout outcome fixtures. The corrected package supersedes those completion claims while preserving that commit in history.
